<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 03 at 3:26AM CST  by NWS Chicago</headline>
<description>...Patchy Icy Spots on Bridges and Overpasses...
Motorists are advised to be alert for icy spots on bridges and
overpasses early this morning. Intermittent freezing drizzle that
developed in the late evening is settling south of the state line
counties, though with temperatures at or below freezing, expect to
encounter some slick spots through the early morning. Leave extra
travel time. Reduce speed and increase following distance,
especially on bridges and overpasses.</description>
